@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .about-us {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .about-us h1 {
                color: #004d99;
                font-size: 40px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                border-bottom: 3px solid #004d99;
                padding-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .about-us h2 {
                color: #0056b3;
                font-size: 32px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                position: relative;
            }

                .about-us h2::before {
                    content: "";
                    position: absolute;
                    left: 0;
                    bottom: -5px;
                    width: 50px;
                    height: 4px;
                    background-color: #0056b3;
                }

            .about-us p {
                line-height: 1.8;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .about-us img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 12px;
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #004d99;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

            .cta-button:hover {
                background-color: #003366;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-us">
            <h1>About Us</h1>

            <p>Welcome to Sterling Global University, a premier institution dedicated to providing top-notch education and fostering a community of learning and growth. Established with a vision to empower students and professionals, our university stands at the forefront of innovation and excellence in education.</p>

            <h2>Our History</h2>
            <p>Founded in 1985, Sterling Global University has evolved into a leading educational institution known for its commitment to academic excellence and holistic development. Our history is marked by a series of milestones that have contributed to our reputation as a center of learning and innovation.</p>

            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to provide a high-quality education that equips students with the knowledge, skills, and values necessary to excel in their chosen fields. We aim to foster an environment of intellectual curiosity, critical thinking, and ethical leadership.</p>

            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>We envision a world where education transforms lives and communities. Sterling Global University strives to be a global leader in education, research, and community engagement, creating opportunities for students to thrive in an ever-changing world.</p>

            <img src="/Content/AboutUsImage.jpg" alt="Sterling Global University Campus">

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
